#: ../../source/index.rst:10
msgid ""
"**IR-SIM** is an open-source, Python-based, lightweight robot simulator "
"designed for navigation, control, and learning. It provides a simple, "
"user-friendly framework with built-in collision detection for modeling "
"robots, sensors, and environments. Ideal for academic and educational "
"use, IR-SIM enables rapid prototyping of robotics and AI algorithms in "
"custom scenarios with minimal coding and hardware requirements."
msgstr ""
"\"\"IR-SIM\"\" 是一款开源、基于 Python "
"的轻量级机器人仿真器，面向导航、控制与学习场景。它提供简单易用的框架，并内置碰撞检测，用于建模机器人、传感器与环境。IR-SIM "
"非常适合科研与教学，可在自定义场景下以最少的编码与硬件需求，快速构建机器人与 AI 算法的原型。"

